patthana17.2:1.1_0: Abyākataṁ vipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo navipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana17.2:2.1_0: Hetuyā tīṇi, adhipatiyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
patthana17.2:3.1_0: Kusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana17.2:3.1_1: Kusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana17.2:3.1_2: Kusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo navipākadhammadhammo ca naakusalo navipākadhammadhammo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana17.2:4.1_0: Akusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana17.2:4.1_1: Akusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana17.2:4.1_2: Akusalaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo navipākadhammadhammo ca naakusalo navipākadhammadhammo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana17.2:5.1_0: Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana17.2:6.1_0: Abyākataṁ nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.

patthana17.2:6.1_2: Abyākataṁ nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo ca naakusalo
